# The build's auto-extract writes the source-language template ({AssemblyName}.en.arb) into each sample's
# Translations folder, exactly as it would for an installed package. It is a generated artifact regenerated
# on every build, so it is not committed. The translated catalogs (de.arb, fr.arb, …) are committed source.
**/Translations/*.en.arb

# The build also emits the catalog manifest (apl-catalogs.json) beside the extracted templates; like them it is
# regenerated on every build and not committed. The WebAssembly sample is the exception — it serves and commits
# its manifest from wwwroot/Translations alongside its translated catalogs, so the sample runs self-contained.
**/Translations/apl-catalogs.json
!**/wwwroot/Translations/apl-catalogs.json
